<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 03:12:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国反弹、美元坚挺，亚洲股市小幅走高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-06/</link><description>亚洲股市周二小幅上涨，得益于遭受重创的中国市场的反弹，尽管由于美联储近期降息的预期减弱，投资者在华尔街下跌后持谨慎态度，这反过来又支撑了美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 02:35:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>独家：外交部长称台湾盟友危地马拉正在考虑与中国建立商业关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-ally-guatemala-mulls-commercial-ties-with-china-foreign-minister-says-2024-02-06/</link><description>中美洲国家危地马拉外交部长周一告诉路透社，危地马拉正在考虑与中国建立正式贸易关系，但计划维持与台湾的现有关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 02:28:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-ally-guatemala-mulls-commercial-ties-with-china-foreign-minister-says-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>寒冷天气阻碍中国游客回家过年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/icy-weather-impedes-travellers-china-home-bound-new-year-festivities-2024-02-06/</link><description>过去一周，寒冷的天气席卷了全国部分地区，冻雨雪冰给中国中部和东部地区的许多人的回家之路带来了困难。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 02:21:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/icy-weather-impedes-travellers-china-home-bound-new-year-festivities-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>日本SMBC聘请前瑞士信贷中国区总裁斯托尔</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/japans-smbc-hires-former-credit-suisse-china-boss-stoehr-2024-02-06/</link><description>日本三井住友银行（SMBC）周二表示，已聘请前瑞士信贷中国区总裁卡斯滕·斯托尔（Carsten Stoehr）担任亚太区副总裁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 02:15:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/japans-smbc-hires-former-credit-suisse-china-boss-stoehr-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>随着降息押注减少，美元站稳近三个月高位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firms-near-3-month-high-rate-cut-bets-dwindle-2024-02-06/</link><description>周二，由于美国国债收益率上升，人们越来越预期美联储今年不太可能大幅降息，美元徘徊在三个月高位附近。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 01:47:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firms-near-3-month-high-rate-cut-bets-dwindle-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>泰国相信援助努力将引发缅甸危机对话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-confident-aid-effort-will-lead-myanmar-crisis-dialogue-2024-02-06/</link><description>泰国一名高级官员表示，泰国领导的一项新的人道主义倡议旨在为军事统治的缅甸交战阵营之间的谈判铺平道路，三年前，一场政变引发了全国各地的不稳定和暴力浪潮。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 00:03:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-confident-aid-effort-will-lead-myanmar-crisis-dialogue-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>总理称中国法院对澳大利亚作家缓刑的判决“令人愤慨”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-courts-suspended-death-sentence-australian-writer-an-outrage-pm-says-2024-02-05/</link><description>澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内塞周二表示，北京法院以间谍罪判处澳大利亚作家杨恒均死刑缓期执行，这“令人愤慨”，并誓言将继续努力争取杨恒均获释。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 22:40:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-courts-suspended-death-sentence-australian-writer-an-outrage-pm-says-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国财政部团队前往中国讨论补贴和经济政策</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-treasury-team-heads-china-this-week-talk-subsidies-economic-policies-2024-02-05/</link><description>一位财政部官员周一表示，拜登政府本周已派出五名美国财政部高级官员前往北京进行经济会谈，其中将包括中国增加过剩工业产能的“非市场”政策。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 22:17:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-treasury-team-heads-china-this-week-talk-subsidies-economic-policies-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：澳洲联储关注美国债券收益率飙升蒙上阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-02-05/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 22:02:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>Stake F1车队以双重身份规避赌博限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/stake-f1-team-swerves-gambling-restrictions-with-dual-identity-2024-02-05/</link><description>索伯运营的 Stake 一级方程式车队本赛季将以两个名字参加比赛，以遵守一些国家的赌博限制。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 20:26:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/stake-f1-team-swerves-gambling-restrictions-with-dual-identity-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟警告不要采取支持太阳能行业的贸易措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-cautions-against-trade-measures-support-solar-sector-2024-02-05/</link><description>欧盟一位高级官员周一表示，在考虑采取任何措施限制光伏电池板、硅片和其他零部件进口之前，欧盟需要考虑其雄心勃勃的太阳能部署目标。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 19:20:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-cautions-against-trade-measures-support-solar-sector-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议院共和党人考虑边境协议，众议院同行敦促拒绝</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/republican-us-senate-border-negotiator-says-party-should-decide-next-move-by-2024-02-05/</link><description>美国参议院两党加强边境安全法案的首席共和党谈判代表表示，他的核心小组应在周二之前决定是否就该提案展开辩论，而众议院共和党领导人则敦促废除该协议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 19:07:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/republican-us-senate-border-negotiator-says-party-should-decide-next-move-by-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国瞄准保证金贷款和卖空以帮助稳定股市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-targets-margin-loans-short-selling-help-stabilise-stocks-2024-02-05/</link><description>中国证监会周一表示，将加强对融资融券、恶意卖空行为的监管，防范质押股票风险。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 16:15:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-targets-margin-loans-short-selling-help-stabilise-stocks-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>分析师预计稀土价格将在 2024 年下半年反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rare-earths-prices-seen-rebounding-second-half-2024-analysts-2024-02-05/</link><description>分析师表示，稀土价格可能已经触底，并有望在今年晚些时候上涨，因为电动汽车和风电的需求以及主要生产国中国预计将取消扩大的产量配额。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:55:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rare-earths-prices-seen-rebounding-second-half-2024-analysts-2024-02-05/</guid></item><item><title>工作忧虑让中国人回家度假心情不好</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/job-worries-sour-mood-chinese-heading-home-holidays-2024-02-05/</link><description>周一，中国工人们挤上火车回家过农历新年假期，他们对工作和经济不景气的担忧给人们期待已久的家庭团聚蒙上了阴影。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 12:31:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/job-worries-sour-mood-chinese-heading-home-holidays-2024-02-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>